    <item>
      <title>英美烟草 (BAT) 21 亿美元的股权出售消除了关键悬而未决，ITC 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/itc-jumps-as-bat-s-2-1-billion-stake-sale-removes-key-overhang</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着英美烟草公司 (British American Tobacco Plc) 开始提出出售这家印度烟草和消费品制造商价值 21 亿美元的股份，该公司 3.6% 的股权以大宗交易方式进行交易，该公司股价创下近四年来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/itc-jumps-as-bat-s-2-1-billion-stake-sale-removes-key-overhang</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔斯社称，无人机袭击后俄罗斯梁赞炼油厂起火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/russia-s-ryazan-refinery-is-on-fire-after-drone-attack-tass-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[无人机袭击后，俄罗斯石油公司最大的炼油厂发生火灾，乌克兰对俄罗斯发动了新的袭击，总统弗拉基米尔·普京声称这是破坏本周总统选举的企图的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/russia-s-ryazan-refinery-is-on-fire-after-drone-attack-tass-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 05:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国担忧升级，铁矿石暴跌考验 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/iron-ore-set-for-100-test-after-slump-on-china-demand-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国的经济前景对炼钢原料构成压力，铁矿石价格延续跌势，期货接近每吨 100 美元的水平，可能会开始挤出成本较高的生产商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/iron-ore-set-for-100-test-after-slump-on-china-demand-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
